    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接充满肾上腺素的体验吧！在 ☀️<strong>《太阳碰撞控制》</strong>☀️是一款刺激的动作街机游戏，在这个危险的宇宙中，你将掌控太阳。移动太阳躲避致命障碍物，收集星星来保持能量，同时迎接越来越艰难的挑战！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a4594f81d61e2bc822545329ed47588a.poster.avif?t=1742987289\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a4594f81d61e2bc822545329ed47588a.webm?t=1742987289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a4594f81d61e2bc822545329ed47588a.mp4?t=1742987289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 躲避超过90种障碍物。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 掌握不同的游戏模式。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 完成特殊任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 升级你的装备。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 将你的名字写在全球排行榜的顶端。   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不同的游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着故事推进，解锁全新的游戏模式。每种模式都有独特的玩法，带给你全新的混乱体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别任务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战独特的特殊任务，以解锁新的关卡与游戏模式。你能完成每个任务吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a559eaf8ec5ca614b6e27f4b8d936792.poster.avif?t=1742987289\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a559eaf8ec5ca614b6e27f4b8d936792.webm?t=1742987289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175690/extras/a559eaf8ec5ca614b6e27f4b8d936792.mp4?t=1742987289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级你的装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级不同的强化道具，提高其正面效果并消除负面影响。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排行榜和成就</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >争夺排行榜的榜首，获得具有挑战性的成就，并证明你控制太阳力量的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
